   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I've been thinking, for a start I think "Relatedly" is a terrible word to use.
How bout "Login with", "Login types" or "Login Methods"  ??

Center the login to the middle of the screen, instead of just using 1/3 of the 
screenspace eg: "Login with a password".
Put all the "Login Methods" in a top menu / dropdown.

Also, we should move "What is OpenID? &amp; "Forgot your password?" out of 
"Relatedly". 

Let's make this login screen spunky....
Create a extraneous links free login page (getting rid of site navigation header 
and footer stuff), with no hatch background - Just have the openhatch logo then 
when logging in maybe a processing cartoon / gif (aldeka) ?

Looking forward to comments.
Paul</pre>
   </td>
